human comprehension.</i>

5
00:01:01,357 --> 00:01:03,788
<i>Though they disappeared
ages ago,</i>

6
00:01:03,890 --> 00:01:07,228
<i>they left behind fragments
of their technology,</i>

7
00:01:07,330 --> 00:01:09,932
<i>scraps that became
the foundation</i>

8
00:01:10,034 --> 00:01:11,499
<i>for all human advancement.</i>

9
00:01:13,369 --> 00:01:15,739
<i>But the Eridians'
greatest secrets</i>

10
00:01:15,841 --> 00:01:17,874
