-<i>Guns, guns, guns!</i>

15
00:01:30,817 --> 00:01:32,647
<i>...fighting
and killing one another</i>

16
00:01:32,749 --> 00:01:34,291
<i>for a chance to find the vault.</i>

17
00:01:37,896 --> 00:01:40,396
<i>But it remained hidden.</i>

18
00:01:42,728 --> 00:01:45,937
<i>Then, amidst
the clouds of chaos,</i>

19
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,964
<i>a glimmer of hope
shone through.</i>

20
00:01:48,905 --> 00:01:50,208
<i>A prophecy.</i>

21
00:01:50,842 --> 00:01:52,241
<i>That one day,</i>

22
00:01:52,344 --> 00:01:55,673
<i>a daughter of Eridia
would open the vault</i>

23
00:01:55,776 --> 00:01:58,777
<i>and restore order
to the broken planet.</i>

24
00:02:01,048 --> 00:02:02,416
<i>Yeah.</i>

25
00:02:02,518 --> 00:02:05,187
<i>That sounds like
some wacko B.S., right?</i>

26
00:02:05,289 --> 00:02:07,159
<i>Well, I thought so too,
until...</i>

27
00:02:08,589 --> 00:02:09,887
