100
00:05:51,308 --> 00:05:53,349
Yeah, well, this sad sack
was the trigger man.

101
00:05:53,451 --> 00:05:54,511
Listen, I never meant
to shoot anyone.

102
00:05:54,613 --> 00:05:56,715
I was...

103
00:05:56,817 --> 00:05:58,456
